data.description: Welcome home to this tastefully renovated two story home featuring 3 bedrooms, 2 full baths and completely finished lower level. This property boasts TWO large decks which look out to your private wooded backyard, perfect to enjoy your morning coffee or entertain friends and family. The lower level features large finished spaces great for an office, family room or guest stay area with its own private bathroom!  Recently upgraded with central AC on the first floor and ductless mini splits on the lower level and fully renovated in 2019 with a new kitchen and new bathrooms. This home is located in the beautiful neighborhood of Continental Village with a private lake, basketball courts, tennis courts and playground just a short distance away. Call today for your private showing!
